                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for synthesizing ethanol and co-producing liquid hydrocarbon through CO2 hydrogenation and iron-based catalyst thereof",
                    "一种CO2加氢合成乙醇联产液态烃的方法及其铁基催化剂"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for synthesizing ethanol and co-producing liquid hydrocarbon through CO2 hydrogenation and an iron-based catalyst thereof, and the method comprises the following steps: taking carbon dioxide and hydrogen as raw materials, and reacting under the conditions of 250-330 DEG C, 3-5 MPa and existence of the catalyst to generate ethanol and liquid hydrocarbon; the catalyst is a supported iron-based catalyst, the active phase of the catalyst comprises Fe, Fe3O4, Fe7C3 and Fe5C2, and the liquid hydrocarbon is hydrocarbon with the carbon number larger than or equal to 5; the volume ratio of the carbon dioxide to the hydrogen is (1: 2)-(1: 5). Based on the iron-based catalyst of a single system, one-step hydrogenation conversion of carbon dioxide into ethanol and liquid hydrocarbon products with high additional values can be realized, and the CO2 conversion rate is gt; the total selectivity gt of ethanol and liquid hydrocarbon is 40%; the selectivity of CO by-products is 1t; and 10%."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种CO2加氢合成乙醇联产液态烃的方法及其铁基催化剂，该方法包括如下步骤：以二氧化碳和氢气为原料，在250‑330℃、3‑5MPa及催化剂存在条件下，反应生成乙醇和液态烃；所述催化剂为负载型铁基催化剂，其活性相组成包括Fe，Fe3O4，Fe7C3以及Fe5C2，所述液态烃为碳数≥5的烃类；所述的二氧化碳和氢气的体积比为1:2‑1:5。本发明基于单一体系的铁基催化剂，即可实现二氧化碳一步加氢转化为高附加值的乙醇和液态烃产品，CO2转化率>40％，乙醇+液态烃的总选择性>50％，CO副产物的选择性<10％。"
                }
            ]
        }
